title: David's New Orleans Style Sno Balls
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Take-out, Southern American, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Quaint little cafe with a laid back atmosphere. Vegetarian friendly include Morning Star brand burgers for New Orleans style po-boys, vegan chick'n patties, vegan flavored sno balls, veggie dogs, and Community Coffee. One of the owners is vegetarian.
